      <title>欧盟财长提高英国清算协议延后至 2028 年的可能性</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-31/eu-finance-chief-albuquerque-raises-prospect-of-uk-clearing-deal-past-2028</link>
      <description><![CDATA[如果市场尚未做好准备，欧盟愿意延长从伦敦夺取欧元清算权的最新期限，这表明欧盟对英国脱欧这一金融领域最具政治影响力的余震之一采取了新的务实态度。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-31/eu-finance-chief-albuquerque-raises-prospect-of-uk-clearing-deal-past-2028</guid>
